WEBVTT

00:06:29.689 --> 00:06:31.963
they started scanning more prisoners,

00:06:31.987 --> 00:06:35.443
serial killers, boys.

00:06:35.467 --> 00:06:36.627
And in all seriousness,

00:06:36.651 --> 00:06:40.985
there was actually a suggestion
that we consider aborting XYY fetuses.

00:06:43.572 --> 00:06:45.056
So in 1980,

00:06:45.080 --> 00:06:48.763
this theory pretty much toppled,
for a number of reasons.

00:06:48.787 --> 00:06:50.482
One,

00:06:50.506 --> 00:06:52.323
there had been this really large study

00:06:52.347 --> 00:06:54.474
that basically showed
there was no connection

00:06:54.498 --> 00:06:56.545
between Y and violence,

00:06:56.569 --> 00:06:58.609
I think we all saw that coming.

00:06:58.633 --> 00:07:00.966
And then, there was one other thing.